Independent\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice Timeis in short supplyforOlympicsprinters but Eugene Amo-Dadzie insists he will not be caught clock-watching.\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice Timeis\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 463}, {\"ngram\": \"short supplyforOlympicsprinters\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"Eugene Amo-Dadzie\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"clock-watching\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Theself-proclaimed world's fastest accountant, 31, is hoping to feature in the fleet of Paris-boundTeam GBstars despite only taking running seriously since he was 26.\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Theself-proclaimed world's fastest accountant\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 614}, {\"ngram\": \"the fleet\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris-boundTeam GBstars\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While his rivals chase PBs and podium finishes 100m star Amo-Dadzie has other priorities - but still backs himself to mix it with the best.\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his rivals\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 753}, {\"ngram\": \"PBs\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 763}, {\"ngram\": \"100m star Amo-Dadzie\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"other priorities\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's one of those things that I like to shout about,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those things\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I very much see myself as a civilian, a normal person, I was working nine to five for however many years and have stepped into the world of elite sport.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 1095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a civilian\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"however many years\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"elite sport\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have got a daughter and another baby on the way and I hope they will be proud and talk about their dad as an athlete as well as a chartered accountant.\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a daughter\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"another baby\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"their dad\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"a chartered accountant\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1250}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's tough at times but it also gives me a competitive advantage in the sense that when I am on the start line, I am not so concerned about the outcome of the race in terms of putting food on the table - a lot of athletes are in that predicament.\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"a competitive advantage\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1318}, {\"ngram\": \"the sense\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"the start line\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1364}, {\"ngram\": \"the outcome\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1455}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1475}, {\"ngram\": \"that predicament\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Working and being an athlete at the same time is something I am very proud about and I feel like it gives me an edge over my opponents.\\\"\", \